OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUvalde school shooting:    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEmbattled police chief is  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fput on leave               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A police chief accused of botching the 
OL,6, response to the fatal shooting of 19   
OL,7, school children and two teachers in    
OL,8, Uvalde, Texas, has been put on leave.  
OL,10,FPedro "Pete" Arredondo, head of the    
OL,11,Fschool district police force, has been 
OL,12,Fblamed for law enforcement delays in   
OL,13,Fconfronting the gunman.                
OL,15,FDefending his actions, the 50-year-old 
OL,16,Fhas said he did not think he was the   
OL,17,Fofficial in charge at the time.        
OL,19,FPublic anger has risen as more details 
OL,20,Fof the 24 May attack emerge.           
